.stitches-sprite(@x: 0, @y: 0, @width: 0, @height: 0) {
    background-position: @x @y;
    width: @width;
    height: @height;
}

.sprite {
    background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,);    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    display: block;

    &.sprite-ballon0 {
        .stitches-sprite(-22px, -22px, 430px, 300px);
    }

    &.sprite-ballon1 {
        .stitches-sprite(-496px, -22px, 468px, 270px);
    }

    &.sprite-ballon2 {
        .stitches-sprite(-1008px, -22px, 400px, 204px);
    }

    &.sprite-ballon3 {
        .stitches-sprite(-1452px, -22px, 491px, 100px);
    }

    &.sprite-ballon4 {
        .stitches-sprite(-1987px, -22px, 400px, 204px);
    }

    &.sprite-ballon5 {
        .stitches-sprite(-2431px, -22px, 490px, 270px);
    }

    &.sprite-ballon6 {
        .stitches-sprite(-2965px, -22px, 420px, 293px);
    }

    &.sprite-github {
        .stitches-sprite(-3429px, -22px, 30px, 30px);
    }

    &.sprite-gmail {
        .stitches-sprite(-3503px, -22px, 30px, 30px);
    }

    &.sprite-linkedin {
        .stitches-sprite(-3577px, -22px, 30px, 30px);
    }

    &.sprite-stackoverflow {
        .stitches-sprite(-3651px, -22px, 30px, 30px);
    }

    &.sprite-tumblr {
        .stitches-sprite(-3725px, -22px, 30px, 30px);
    }

    &.sprite-twitter {
        .stitches-sprite(-3799px, -22px, 30px, 30px);
    }
}
